{"tid":499160,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"愈大就愈少機會去玩去顛","createTime":"2017-12-14T13:19:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-14T13:23:12.000Z","uid":143774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"afff6a81bccff82a09b85c24ab02bf78088d6686","tid":499160,"uid":143774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T13:19:31.000Z","msg":"返工放工完全想係屋企hea 同訓，唔想去旅遊<br />\n<br />\n嘩，咁樣危唔危險架 / 屌，好貴喎&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n呢啲嘢成日係腦海出現，去阻止自己<br />\n<br />\n返工放工考試返學，又係咁，日子過得一式一樣，感覺上人生梗係差咗少少野咁<br />\n<br />\n之前有過幾大的夢想，口口聲聲向目標進步，但當進發緊個時，反而好似愈嚟愈遠，已經唔再係曾經好天真，一往無懼嘅小孩<br />\n<br />\n呢個夢想真係唔係可以當飯食咁，未去到，已經要諗緊好多問題，現實總是逆流而行<br />\n<br />\n可能我個人生一開始已經係地獄級"},{"pid":"30720dfb5ee2194e4c02f093240511c44df42fb6","tid":499160,"uid":143774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T13:21:09.000Z","msg":"利申：而家仲未放棄爭扎，仲好想發一場夢，人生幾何呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a26e93ac73499522547247dd7fb93d40747e263","tid":499160,"uid":49245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T13:21:37.000Z","msg":"Agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fb24af6970af4b5ef275d87afcf834296face63","tid":499160,"uid":143774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T13:22:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n加油呀爸打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f7d8a065a7f0992996396f23491cc471250da9f","tid":499160,"uid":143774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T13:23:12.000Z","msg":"我打完篇野先發覺同標題完全不符<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}